label: Diary of a voyage from New York to California and return trip by train, 1874-1875

metadata.label: Title
value: Diary of a voyage from New York to California and return trip by train, 1874-1875

metadata.label: Extent
value: 1 v. (137 p.): ill., maps; (0.5 linear ft.)

metadata.label: Description
value: The volume includes illustrations of California, Nevada, and Niagara Falls as well as maps of the railroad routes. There is a list of the illustrations and a list of plants identified. The author also created an abstract of the diary in the back of the volume.
